| I wrote this to try to debug the mapping between pipes and endpoints on the Mac.

: choose4  nth count type space  2drop 2drop ;

: .ep-dir   push  z" both"  z" unknown"  z" in"  z" out"  pop choose4 ;
: .ep-type  push  z" interrupt"  z" bulk"  z" isoch"  z" control"  pop choose4 ;

: .pipe  ( direction number transferType maxpacketsize interval pipe#)
   cr  u.  drop  u.  .ep-type  u.  .ep-dir ;

: .pipes  ( device)
   radix preserve decimal
   32 0 do  i over usb-get-pipe-properties  0= if leave then  i .pipe  loop  drop ;
